Package: chatr
Type: Package
Title: Send text, R code and R objects to 'ChatWork'.
Version: 0.0.0.9
Author: Sugiaki1989
Maintainer: Sugiaki1989 <sugiaki@gmail.com>
Description: This package is based on slackr and made for ChatWork.ChatWork provides a service for teams to collaborate by sharing messages, images, links, files and more. chatr functions in this package are provided that make it possible to interact with the ChatWork API. 
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 3.6.3)
Imports:
    httr (>= 1.4.1),
    config (>= 0.3)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
